rows.label: qev015702_MSG0001
rows.name: Hey! Little help over here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0002
rows.name:
Some indigen attacked us during our assignment.
Got one of my men pretty good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0003
rows.name:
Skell is busted, too. Damn thing won't move at all.
Think maybe you could spare some supplies?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0004
rows.name: ...Oh, Satie sent you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, why didn't you say so instead of letting me flap
my gums like an idiot? Here, gimme the supplies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0006
rows.name: I need to get this Skell patched pronto.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0007
rows.name: Thanks, pal. You're a lifesaver.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0008
rows.name:
I asked Satie for help, but I wasn't exactly getting my
hopes up. Know what I mean?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0009
rows.name: I'm impressed you made it out here in one piece.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: NewText_11
rows.name: Brag

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0010
rows.name: Say how easy the trip was for a BLADE like yourself.

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0011
rows.name: Downplay

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0012
rows.name: Shrug and tell Myles that you got lucky.

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0013
rows.name:
...That supposed to be a dig? You diggin' at us?
'Cause I don't like the cut of your jib![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0014
rows.name:
Hell, if that giant indigen thing hadn't turned up,
I'd be home slamming down a cold one right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0015
rows.name: Lucky. Right. Well, we sure as hell weren't.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0016
rows.name: That indigen turned up outta nowhere.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0017
rows.name:
How the heck did you beat the whimsical duoguill,
anyway? That thing was huge![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0018
rows.name:
What? You made it all the way here without running
into it? Not even once?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0019
rows.name:
Yeesh. Either somebody's watching out for you,
or somebody's got it in for us. One or the other...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0020
rows.name:
Wait. That means that damn whimsical duoguill's
still on the rampage somewhere.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0021
rows.name: Talk about a piece of bad news...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0022
rows.name: Not every BLADE's as lucky as you, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0023
rows.name: We've got to take that thing out before it kills someone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0024
rows.name:
What do you say? Think that luck of yours is good
enough to beat a whimsical duoguill?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0027
rows.name: Me? I want to sock the giant lug right in its ugly face.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0028
rows.name:
I'm sure you know how frustrating it is to have your
assignment put on hold.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0029
rows.name:
Do this for a fellow BLADE. Secure the route and kick
that ugly thing right in the teeth.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0030
rows.name: I'll be here waiting for all the juicy details.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0031
rows.name: Hey! Little help over here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0032
rows.name:
Some indigen attacked us during our assignment.
Got one of my men pretty good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0033
rows.name:
Skell is busted, too. Damn thing won't move at all.
Think maybe you could spare some supplies?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0034
rows.name: ...Oh, Satie sent you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0035
rows.name:
Well, why didn't you say so instead of letting me flap
my gums like an idiot? Here, gimme the supplies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0036
rows.name: I need to get this Skell patched pronto.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0037
rows.name: Thanks, pal. You're a lifesaver.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0038
rows.name:
I asked Satie for help, but I wasn't exactly getting my
hopes up. Know what I mean?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0039
rows.name:
But she really outdid herself. I never would have
guessed she'd net a pro like you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0040
rows.name:
And thanks to you, we can get back to work.
Haven't even lost much time![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0041
rows.name:
We'll bang these data probes in at the FrontierNav
probe sites and be back home in time for supper.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0042
rows.name:
Hopefully the indigen data they churn out will make
sure no one else gets another nasty surprise.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_JNK0010
rows.name: Support[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_SEL0011
rows.name: Give Myles's plan the thumbs-up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_JNK0020
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_SEL0021
rows.name:
Ask Myles where the FrontierNav
probe placement sites are.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0043
rows.name: Hey, thanks![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0044
rows.name:
The Pathfinders are an elite group even by BLADE
standards, which means average schlubs like me
have gotta work extra hard to keep up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0045
rows.name:
And THAT means it's time for me to patch this Skell up
and get back to work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0046
rows.name:
One's just a ways northwest of here,
on the shore of a lake.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0047
rows.name: The other one's in a cave to the northeast.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0048
rows.name:
I was thinking my team could snatch 'em both up
before all this happened.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0049
rows.name:
If you're headed that way, they're all yours.
Just be careful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0050
rows.name: Some planet we picked to crash into, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0051
rows.name:
Heh. It's easy to forget how nuts this place is until you
get your ass handed to you by some giant monster.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0052
rows.name:
I mean, for the foreseeable future, we're probably
gonna be fighting things that can easily crush Skells.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0053
rows.name:
I gotta remember to be a lot more careful,
or I'm gonna wind up a lot more dead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0054
rows.name: No more rookie mistakes for me from here on out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev015702_MSG0055
rows.name:
You be careful too, yeah? Let's the both of us live a
long, long time. See where humanity goes, you know?[ST:wait ]
